						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying in the Hiri-maṭha.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Late characters.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragmentary record seems to refer to a well, probably excavated by Harabīraya in the premises of Hiri-maṭa <hi rend="italic">(maṭha).</hi> There is a reference to 12 mana <hi rend="italic">(māna)</hi> at the beginning and 41 ba <hi rend="italic">(baḷḷa)</hi> at the end.</p>						

						<p>It is in late characters of the 18th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
